sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant PG as PostgreSQL Executor
    participant IDX as Index
    participant HEAP as Table (Heap)

    App->>PG: Submit query with WHERE clause
    PG->>IDX: Search index for matching entries
    loop For each matching index entry
        IDX-->>PG: Return row pointer (TID)
        PG->>HEAP: Fetch row from heap using TID
        HEAP-->>PG: Return row data
        PG-->>App: Return row (if matches visibility and query)
    end
    PG-->>App: Return result set
